        <profileDesc>
            <creation/>
            <abstract>
                <p>Medico-magic prescriptions against various diseases (especially against female or gynaeocological diseases) as well as demons of
                    a similar type and content as those edited in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7T7W7L3J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><title level="m">Médecine et plantes d’Éthiopie. Les traités médicaux éthiopiens. Medycyna i zioła etiopskie. Etiopskie traktaty medyczne</title><title level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Warszawa</pubPlace><publisher>Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe</publisher><date>1968</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</t:title></series><biblScope unit="volume">XIV</biblScope></bibl>
                    and of a similar type as <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7544Prescr">LIT7544Prescr</ref>, <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7545MedPres">LIT7545MedPres</ref> 
                    and <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7546MedPrescr">LIT7546MedPrescr</ref>, which are attested in the same manuscript 
                    (cf. <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient12034">London, British Library, BL Oriental 12034</ref>).</p>
            </abstract>
